videos.headline: Aggies go end-to-end with 95-yard TD
videos.description: Facing 3rd-and-9 from its own 5 yard line, Texas A&M's Kyle Allen finds Josh Reynolds streaking down the sideline for a 95-yard touchdown to increase the Aggies lead at 13-0.
